### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = 

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### App Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "displayName": "Test User",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

